---
title: BBQ Pulled Chicken Sandwiches with Tangy Cabbage Slaw
description: Southern barbecue is famous for its tangy, vinegar-based sauce, and this DIY version, which is tossed with juicy pulled chicken, will have you ditching the bottled kind. Pile it all on brioche buns with a little bit of spring mix for that essential 'crunch'!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sandwichs-au-poulet-effiloche-bbq-12beb310.jpg
